ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisORDER RESPECTING EX-GRATIA PAYMENTS TO CHINESE HEAD TAX PAYERS - which authorizes the making of ex gratia payments to people who paid a head tax under An Act to Restrict and Regulate Chinese Immigration into Canada (S.C. 1885, c. 71) or under An Act Respecting the Immigration of Chinese Persons, chapter 2 of the Statutes of Newfoundland of 1906.
